spi: pxa2xx: Reuse int_error_stop() in pxa2xx_spi_slave_abort()

It appears that pxa2xx_spi_slave_abort()almost  repeats the functionality
of the int_error_stop(). Reuse int_error_stop() in pxa2xx_spi_slave_abort().

